{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"55eb0b33ed","title":"在抗大的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ed4616a362","index":0,"year":1938,"month":12,"day":13,"articleId":"55eb0b33ed"}],"tags":[{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui2","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1943-1949卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui2a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b9b352032d","type":"title","text":"在抗大的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"55eb0b33ed"},{"id":"90bed8c557","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央六中全会估计到广州武汉失守以后，战争形势要逐渐进入新阶段，我们的任务就在于如何增加力量来停止敌之进攻，准备我之反攻。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"55eb0b33ed"},{"id":"a553538f44","type":"paragraph","text":"这里，最基本的推动全盘工作的正确方针是培植干部。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"55eb0b33ed"},{"id":"b85bede195","type":"paragraph","text":"在今天，广大的敌人占领区域没有普遍的游击队的活动，千百万群众没有人去组织，去领导他们进行抗日战争。这就是说，中国还有很多地方，没有共产党，没有抗日武装，没有把这些生动力量统统都发掘和发挥出来，这些工作都要人去做的。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"55eb0b33ed"}],"page":{"id":"139148b59a","publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"55eb0b33ed","start":453,"end":453}}}},"__N_SSG":true}